text: Hai ureueng mukmin ‘oh tameukawen Tacre inong nyan leupah that bagah Gohlom seuteuboh gata deungon jih s Teuma ateuh jih hana peue ‘iddah Hana peue jipreh ‘iddah bak gata Teuma le gata tabri hadiyah Tabri keu jihnyan peuseunang ate Beuthat tameucre bek jeut keu susah Beu jroh sama jroh watee tameucre
